{"tid":774607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國解除對遊戲使用納粹卍字的禁令","createTime":"2018-08-10T12:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T15:28:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53189505ae444a843016a4c6a1ac0e1fab3d2a2b","tid":774607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"2018/08/10 16:42<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews&d=idlRQUqkF3qAdBQ7IAyxfUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0a1bb4d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news</a> ... ymbols-video-games/<br />\n<br />\n德國的刑法禁止刻畫任何反憲法的符號，其中包括納粹卍字符號。但藝術作品除外，描述二戰的德國電影允許使用納粹符號。此外，研究、歷史或科學目的的材料也豁免於禁令。現在，視頻遊戲作品也被視為是一種藝術作品類型，允許使用納粹符號。去年發佈的替代歷史遊戲《Wolfenstein II》為了在德國發行而修改了納粹符號，引發了遊戲界的爭論，認為遊戲也應該像電影一樣對待。"},{"pid":"88ed05c19edc11529df4512659e95e3a6895d608","tid":774607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"很多別有用心的勢力用遊戲來滲透傳播一些不正確的歷史信息。"},{"pid":"dd2dab9f40ab001f1c41ea608ce6a203738d036e","tid":774607,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"sieg heil"},{"pid":"1a9cce56dbe7f569366a1eeb9dc940f1f23157e1","tid":774607,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67ca910f615d90d6c9781c85cbf5cc03770a9974","tid":774607,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67c4a8f4cce7d32472593cc0d84e3b4a67b60e62","tid":774607,"uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"左到盡頭開始要變右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d0df01abd84ca099dbf4e98bf2997c3d7e2a3f","tid":774607,"uid":60695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88ed05c19edc11529df4512659e95e3a6895d608","tid":